  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bae\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A yellow rescue that was brought into the country illegally",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A batch of turmeric and disinfectant, which was brought into the country illegally, was recovered by the army at around 11.00 pm yesterday (04) in Gautharimunya forest area under Kilinochchi Poonagari police division.",
        "Based on a secret information received by the Military Intelligence Branch, the soldiers of 66 Barracks have been recovered and handed over to Poonagri Police.",
        "2,000 kg of turmeric hidden in 65 big bags and pesticides in 03 bags were seized in the raid based on information received by the Military Intelligence Unit about the illegal importation of goods by sea.",
        "It is suspected that this quantity of turmeric and pesticides have been brought to the country from India and the Poonagri police are conducting further investigations to arrest the suspects."
      ],
